  "prompt": "How do I make friends in office?",
  "response": "Here are some tips to make friends in the office:\n\n1. Be friendly and approachable\n- Smile and greet colleagues\n- Engage in small talk\n- Show genuine interest in others\n\n2. Participate in office social events\n- Join team lunches\n- Attend company happy hours\n- Participate in team-building activities\n\n3. Offer help and support\n- Assist colleagues with work tasks\n- Be collaborative and team-oriented\n- Share knowledge and resources\n\n4. Find common interests\n- Discuss hobbies, sports, or shared experiences\n- Join workplace clubs or interest groups\n- Connect on professional networking platforms\n\n5. Communicate effectively\n- Be a good listener\n- Ask open-ended questions\n- Respect boundaries and professional etiquette\n\n6. Be positive and professional\n- Maintain a positive attitude\n- Avoid office gossip\n- Be reliable and trustworthy\n\n7. Connect outside work\n- Grab coffee or lunch together\n- Invite colleagues to casual after-work activities\n- Connect on social media platforms\n\n8. Attend networking events\n- Company-sponsored events\n- Professional conferences\n- Industry meetups\n\nRemember to be genuine, patient, and respectful while building workplace relationships.",
